Comment: This is generally considered unsound and called the Boden-Kieseritzky Gambit. Black's typical replies are 4. ... Nxc3 or 4. ... Nc6 both generally leading to good games for Black although there are dangers. I was not aware of this particularly gambit at the time and proceeded differently.
